# Project 1

## Objective

Create a device group inside Microsoft Defender for Endpoint.

## Environment

Microsoft Defender for Endpoint Trial

## Steps

1. Login to Microsoft Defender Portal

2. Navigate to

Settings

↓

Endpoints

↓

Permissions

↓

Device Groups

3. Click Add Device Group

4. Enter

Name

Description

Automation Level

5. Save

## Result

The device group was created successfully.

## Skills Learned

Device Management

Automation

RBAC

Microsoft Defender Portal
